#: ../../minio.rst:10
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../minio.rst:12
msgid ""
"MinIO needs two dedicated virtual host, a FQDN like ``minio-"
"api.nethserver.org`` and ``minio-ui.nethserver.org``."
